==Type 815A== After year 2000, an improved version appeared, designated as '''Type 815A''', and the most obvious external visual difference between '''Type 815A''' and earlier Type 815 is that the former has a different mast somewhat similar to a pagoda shape, and the sheer line is curved at a greater angle.<ref>[http://www.haijun360.com/news/dzZCC/2011/1122/1111222111414906C8I6H50E4FHKJ8H5.html Type 815A]</ref>
